From c1c522ba1fe66d2c9a0bd6c79e839a39649e7639 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Galih Tama <galpt@v.recipes>
Date: Fri, 26 Jun 2026 17:55:26 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] infinity-scheduler v3: EMA slice modulation + EEVDF surgery

Complete v3 patch including:
- update_deadline(): infinity_slice() for EMA-modulated slice (FIX:
  this function was dead code since v1, never called)
- update_curr(): infinity_consume() for EMA tracking
- pick_eevdf(): protect_slice bypass when EMA > 50%
- place_entity(): EMA-modulated wakeup vslice for low-EMA tasks
- enqueue_task_fair(): infinity_wakeup() EMA decay
- dequeue_task_fair(): sleep timestamp tracking
- pick_next_entity(): NULL guard
- task_fork_fair(): infinity_fork_init()
- RT EMA modulation and sysctl infrastructure

Signed-off-by: Galih Tama <galpt@v.recipes>
---
